title: Vege Life Cafe
description: Specialties include 'lui chai' which has a leafy vegetable with mint leave soup and brown rice with small accompaniments of veggies, nut, sesame seeds, etc.; nasi lemak (coconut milk rice with nuts and veggies); Taiwanese noodle soups.  In 2015 relocated here from 2 Jalan SS26/6, Taman Mayang Jaya. Please send exact map coordinates of new location to happycow!
streetAddress: Shoplots near Kelana Jaya LRT station, facing LDP
